commit.message:
svr3gas.h (EXTRA_SECTIONS): Delete in_bss.

	* i386/svr3gas.h (EXTRA_SECTIONS): Delete in_bss.
	(EXTRA_SECTION_FUNCTIONS): Delete BSS_SECTION_FUNCTION.
	(BSS_SECTION_FUNCTION): Delete.

From-SVN: r11375
